How to install PAPI on your system
----------------------------------

1) Pick the appropriate Makefile.<arch> for your system and compile.
   OPTIONAL: Edit the Makefile.<arch>
   % make -f Makefile.<arch>
2) Check for errors. Look for the libpapi.a and libpapi.so 
   in the current directory.
   OPTIONAL: Run the test programs in ftests/ and tests/
3) Install the distribution where desired.
   % make -f Makefile.<arch> DESTDIR=<dir where papi tree is to be installed>

